      <abstract>
        <p>Yen drop amid worries about Japanese economy; list of international currency exchange rates (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>THE YEN FALLS. The yen dropped as recent bankruptcies and a stock market slide cast doubt on the strength of Japan's economy. In New York, the dollar settled at 108.88 yen, up from 107.67 on Thursday.</p>
